        "summary": "Aggregate computes count and numeric aggregations (sum/avg/min/max) over the\nlive records matching the same Filter as Find, optionally grouped by a field.\nIt server-streams one message per group; a plain (ungrouped) aggregation\nstreams a single message. Aggregation runs entirely in the engine — the\ncollection is never materialised on the client.",
        "operationId": "FileDB_Aggregate",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "A successful response.(streaming responses)",
            "schema": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
